short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Keep track of your Etherpad pads.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Etherpad Tracker keeps track of your Etherpad pads, as you may have guessed.

Just configure the URL of your Etherpad instance and the Etherpad Tracker will automatically recognize and remember pads you visit. It provides you with a maintainable list that you can search your pads and manage your favorites.
